                    <p><i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-fw fa-list"></i><a target="_blank" title="另開新視窗" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.epa.gov.tw/Page/70E67DE2079DF931">隱私權及資訊安全宣告</a></p>
                    <p><i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-fw fa-info"></i><a target="_blank" title="另開新視窗" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.epa.gov.tw/Page/A33D3A6556ABFCD2">網站資料開放宣告</a></p>
                    <p><i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-fw fa-phone"></i><strong>諮詢電話：</strong>@SysConfig.Cfg.SupportPhone</p>
                    <p><i class="fa fa-fw fa-clock"></i><strong>諮詢時間：</strong> 09:00-17:00</p>
                    <p><i aria-hidden="true" class="fa fa-fw fa-envelope"></i><a href="~/ContactUs">諮詢信箱</a></p>
